        <div>
            <h2>About</h2>
        </div>
            <div class="blurb">
                <h3><i>The Hermetic Exchange is a two way marketplace for the intrepid interdimensional wizard, wishing to buy and/or sell magical wares and test their power against the infinite rifts.</i></h3>
            <br>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <p>Create an account and join the fun in this small game about finding/buying/selling virtual magical items.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>Once you sign up, take a look at your inventory and equip your items to increase your power level!</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>Explore the rift, claim your daily reward, (maybe equip that too), and try your luck with your daily rifts</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>Visit your inventory and list your items on the market, if someone buys them you'll gaine credits!</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>Visit the Exchange to see what premium items are for sale, and search for user listed items in the search bar!</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>Visit the user search page to look for other users by name or email address!</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>Click on Buy Credits and purchase virtual money with real money!</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
